title: Looking for Duo Partner to Level 30
body:
Hi 

You can Add me: Rouise - I am currently Level 10 looking for a duo partner just to make the game a little more enjoyable up until Level 30. I am new to the game and also need tips.

Thank you

replies.body:
You should take a look at this website 
http://www.lol-coaching.com/newbie.php
Can get a free mentor.
I am lvl 30 but still new to the game. I will gladly help you learn about the game. Feel free to message me when you want. Ask anything and I will most likely know the answer
Sure, i have an unranked smurf so we don't have to play against higher level players, add me if you're interested
